{"word":"ἀπαύγασμα","slug":"ἀπαύγασμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπαύγασμα, ατος, τό</el></b> [<el>ἀπαυγάζω</el> (<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:αὐγή\">αὐγή</a></el>) ‘radiate, reflect’] ‘brightness coming from a source’, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b><i>radiance, brilliance</i> <a href='B:650 1:3'>Hb 1:3</a>;</b> here some scholars prefer the passive sense, <b><i>reflection.</i></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπάτωρ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπαφρίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}